        {
            "title": "中國對高通公司收購Autotalks的交易啟動反托辣斯調查",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國國家市場監督管理總局周五宣布，已對高通公司收購Autotalks啟動反托辣斯調查。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家美國晶片製造商於6月宣布了該收購交易。根據聲明，市場監管總局將調查高通此次收購是否違反中國反托辣斯法。消息公佈後，高通股價在紐約盤前交易中下跌4%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Opens Antitrust Probe of Qualcomm’s Autotalks Deal</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9A%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BCautotalks%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E5%8F%8D%E6%89%98%E8%BE%A3%E6%96%AF%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-092811979.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-10 18:00:48",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中港股市齊挫　恒指曾瀉逾500點　上證失守3900點｜恒生指數",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"中港股市今日表現疲弱，其中恒指午後一度跌逾500點。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/COfm2izMqYnh55YGEuxPAg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/am730_578/6abff3a012a92f2e95db4569fdef2575\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中港股市今日表現疲弱，其中恒指午後一度跌逾500點。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>中港股市今日(10日)表現疲弱，其中港股低開逾200點後節節向下，</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>午後跌幅更持續擴大，最多跌逾500點，低見26,247點，收市報26,290點，跌462點，大市成交3,337億元，連跌5個交易日；國企指數9,358點，跌171點；恒生科技指數6,259點，跌211點。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>恒指成份股方面，其中藥明生物(2269)跌逾7%，報37.86元，是全日跌幅最大藍籌；同系的藥明康德(2359)跌近6%，報112.4元。至於獲提私有化的恒生(011)微升0.6元，報150.4元；滙豐(005)跌0.5元，報103.5元。</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ee5ca512-3bc3-3bd8-a296-233ee932dcb3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>內地股市方面，上證指數收市報3,897點，跌36點或0.9%，失守3,900點；深證成指收市報13,355點，跌370點或2.7%；創業板指數更跌4.55%或148點，報3,113.26點。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/中港股市齊挫-恒指曾瀉逾500點-上證失守3900點-恒生指數/607483?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/中港股市齊挫-恒指曾瀉逾500點-上證失守3900點-恒生指數/607483?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/中港股市齊挫-恒指曾瀉逾500點-上證失守3900點-恒生指數/607483?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E9%BD%8A%E6%8C%AB-%E6%81%92%E6%8C%87%E6%9B%BE%E7%80%89%E9%80%BE500%E9%BB%9E-%E4%B8%8A%E8%AD%89%E5%A4%B1%E5%AE%883900%E9%BB%9E-%E6%81%92%E7%94%9F%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8-092600496.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-10 17:35:50",
